description: About 275 places are pending inclusion on the Isle of Man's register for protected buildings.
title: Proposed listed sites could be at risk if named, says minister
title_page: Proposed listed sites could be at risk if named, says minister - BBC News
maintext: The Isle of Man's protected register is similar to the United Kingdom's process of listing buildings, but it is a blanket system rather than the graded one used in the UK.
